<div class="row">
	<div class="col s12">
		<ul class="tabs tabs-fixed-width">
			<li class="tab"><a href="#" class="active">Resumen</a></li>
			<li class="tab"><a href="#" class="lime-text" onclick="apretaste.send({command: 'CORONAVIRUS ENFERMOS'})">E</a></li> 
			<li class="tab"><a href="#" class="red-text" onclick="apretaste.send({command: 'CORONAVIRUS MUERTES'})">M</a></li> 
			<li class="tab"><a href="#" class="green-text" onclick="apretaste.send({command: 'CORONAVIRUS RECUPERADOS'})">R</a></li> 
		</ul>

		<p>Estado global del coronavirus según el "Novel Coronavirus (nCoV) Data Repository". Última actualización el <%= updated %>.</p>

		<ul class="collection">
			<li class="collection-item avatar">
				<i class="material-icons circle lime lighten-3 black-text">add_alert</i>
				<span class="title label">Enfermos</span>
				<p class="number lime-text"><%= confirmed %></p>
				<a href="#!" class="secondary-content" onclick="apretaste.send({command: 'CORONAVIRUS ENFERMOS'})"><i class="material-icons">arrow_forward</i></a>
			</li>

			<li class="collection-item avatar">
				<i class="material-icons circle red lighten-3 black-text">airline_seat_flat</i>
				<span class="title label">Muertes</span>
				<p class="number red-text"><%= deaths %></p>
				<a href="#!" class="secondary-content" onclick="apretaste.send({command: 'CORONAVIRUS MUERTES'})"><i class="material-icons">arrow_forward</i></a>
			</li>

			<li class="collection-item avatar">
				<i class="material-icons circle green lighten-3 black-text">assignment_turned_in</i>
				<span class="title label">Recuperados</span>
				<p class="number green-text"><%= recovered %></p>
				<a href="#!" class="secondary-content" onclick="apretaste.send({command: 'CORONAVIRUS RECUPERADOS'})"><i class="material-icons">arrow_forward</i></a>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div>